 stickum used in the stamps can help determine if the poisoning was an accident or intentional.&#10;4. Prepare Antidote and Medical Information: The antidote for the poison should be prepared, and medical information related to the cure should be made available to doctors as soon as possible.&#10;5. Release Propaganda: Releasing propaganda about the United States &quot;whipping&quot; the mystery virus can help maintain public morale and confidence during this critical situation.&#10;6. International Gesture: Sending a stamp collection to the Kremlin can serve as an international gesture and potentially help in resolving the crisis or gaining support from other nations.&#10;7. Investigate Source of Poison: Continue investigating the source of the poisoning with high priority and cooperation from officers, utilizing expertise to identify the cause of the epidemic.">
